      "text": "Be quick to an-tic-i-pate__ our foes___ ere we be en-slaved__ by them__ that blas-pheme__ Thee and__ that men---ace us____ with__ their___ threats, O mer-ci-ful Christ___ our God; by Thy__ Cross de--feat them that___ op--pose__ us that they___ may know___ how might---y___ is the faith____ of Or---tho--dox__ Chris-----tians, through Thy pure Moth-er’s prayers for us__ all, O on-ly___ Friend of__ man.__"
